'''''Winnie''''', ni filime yerekana ubuzima bwa Sinema yo muri Afrika yepfo yasohotse muri 2017 yayobowe na Pascale Lamche ikanakorwa na Christoph Jörg na Steven Markovitz kuri Pumpernickel Films, Submarine Films, Big World Cinema. 

Iyi filime ivuga ku buzima bwa Winnie Madikizela-Mandela n'urugamba rwe adacogora rwo gukuraho Apartheid muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo.   Iyi filime yerekanwe mu rwego rwo kwerekana iserukiramuco ry'uburenganzira bwa muntu 2019.  Muri uwo mwaka, Lamche yatsindiye igihembo cy'umuyobozi mwiza wa documentaire mpuzamahanga mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance .  Yatowe kandi muri Afurika Movie Academy Awards ibihembo bya Documentaire nziza.

